modShortDescription: Replica models of all zombies and animals found in the world for display purposes thru out your home/base. Or like a trophy of what you have killed.
modDescription:
Replica models of all [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) and [animals](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-animals/) found in the world for display purposes thru out your home/base. Or like a trophy of what you have killed.

## Changelog

* **_(new)_** Removed hostile template.
* Updated to remove the extra rubbish.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/stallionsden/Valmar-Modlets/tree/master/Valmars%20Zombie%20Display)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20079-valmars-a19-modlets/).
